<body>
  <div class="wallpaper">
    <div class="white diagonal-box">
      <%= image_tag "star005.png", class: "rotation margin"%>
      <%= image_tag "star003.png", class: "scale"%>
      <%= image_tag "star002.png", class: "rotation margin"%>
      <%= image_tag "star004.png", class: "scale"%>
      <%= image_tag "star005.png", class: "rotation margin"%>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-vertical">
      <h1 class="big-text black">Think <span class="gold">legacy</span> with us</h1>
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="margin">
          <h3>We are a <span class="border-bottom">local family</span> that would like to show you
            around our town in a unique way. Fed by several areas of knowledge and different approaches to reality,
          we will journey simultaneously through memory and through some of the most
          relevant issues of our times.</h3>
          <h3>Our tours are participatory, so not only do we invite you to explore our living
          spaces but your own inner worlds. You don't have to be or know anything in
          particular, just <span class="border-bottom">relax and enjoy.</span></h3>
        </div>
        <div class="flex margin" style="margin-top: 100px">
          <%= image_tag "star001.png", class: "rotation margin opacity"%>
          <h1 class="gold margin">Even a slight 1º change in perspective can drastically affect the final trajectory</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="diagonal-box">How to be a good ancestor?</p>

    </div>
  <div>
  <div class="pink block">
    <h1 class="dark-gray">GUIDES</h1>
    <h2>Mariana Galán</h2>
    <span>MA in Social Sculpture</span>
    <p>Imaginative, nonconformist, resourceful</p>
    <h2>Francisco Galán</h2>
    <span>MA in Philosophy</span>
    <p>Razor-sharp logic, insightful, playful</p>
    <h2>Genevieve Galán</h2>
    <span>PhD in History</span>
    <p>Witty, profound, welcoming</p>
  </div>

  <h1>Tours</h1>
  <h2>Book now!</h2>
  <% @tours.each do |tour|%>
    <h3><%= link_to tour.name.capitalize, tour_path(tour) %></h3>
  <% end %>
  <p>Moral dilemmas: choose your adventure</p>
  <p>About Cars</p>
  <p>The abandoned spaces</p>
</body>
